high_descs: Go to the wall, turn left, walk past the counter on the left, turn left after passing the counter, before the counter on the left ends turn right and face the counter.
Take the knife above the fork from the counter.
Go left to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Go left to the fridge.
Put the knife on the upper shelf in the bottom compartment of the fridge.
Go right back to the counter with the potato.
Take a slice of potato.
Turn around, go to the sink that is to the right of the oven.
Put the potato in the sink. Wash the potato. Take the potato from the sink.
Turn right, go back to the fridge, turn right, go to the wall, turn left to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of potato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and left again to reach the counter with the fork and the knife.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter over top the fork.
Turn around with the knife then back around to see the potato on the counter.
Slice up the potato with the knife.
Take the knife and turn to the left so you are standing in front of the fridge.
Open the door to the fridge and place the knife on the shelf.
Shut the fridge door and turn right to go back to the potato on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the sliced potato.
Take the piece of potato and turn left and go towards the sink.
Place the potato in the sink and turn the water on to clean it then turn it off. Pick up the piece of potato again.
Turn around and head right then left towards the microwave.
Place the potato on the plate and shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Cutting up a potato and putting it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk straight to wall, turn left, walk straight to microwave, turn left, walk straight towards the end of the counter
Turn right, walk straight to the counter, grab the knife behind the fork
Turn around, walk straight to counter, then turn right, walk straight towards the door, turn right next to the fridge
Look down at potato, cut the potato with the knife
Turn left, walk straight in front of fridge, turn right
Open fridge door, place knife on top shelf
Shut the fridge door, turn right, walk straight, then turn left
Grab slice of potato
Turn left, walk straight towards door, turn left, walk straight next to the oven, turn right at the sink
Look down, place potato slice in sink, turn on the faucet, turn off, pick up potato slice from sink
Turn right towards the fridge, turn right again, walk straight towards wall, turn left, walk straight towards microwave
Open microwave door, place potato slice in microwave, shut the door
anns.task_desc: Put a potato slice in the microwave
